{
  "title": "Plugin Platform — Student Management",
  "uid": "sm-plugin-platform",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "tags": ["student-management", "plugin"],
  "timezone": "Asia/Shanghai",
  "refresh": "60s",
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Uptime",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0},
      "targets": [{"expr": "process_uptime_seconds"}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s"}}
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Start Time",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 0},
      "targets": [{"expr": "process_start_time_seconds * 1000"}],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "dateTimeAsIso"}}
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total Plugin API Calls (1h)",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 0},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "sum(increase(http_server_requests_seconds_count{uri=~\"/api/plugin-platform.*\"}[1h]))"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Plugin Overview API QPS",
      "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 0},
      "targets": [
        {"expr": "rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{uri=\"/api/plugin-platform/overview\"}[5m])"}
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "reqps"}}
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Notes",
      "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 4},
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Plugin Platform 监控\n- **Uptime** / **Start Time**: JVM 实例运行与启动时刻\n- **Plugin API Calls**: 最近 1 小时 `/api/plugin-platform/*` 累计\n\n### 进一步埋点 (TODO)\n业务维度指标 `plugin_loaded_total{code}` / `plugin_enabled{code}` 待 ContributionDispatcher/PluginPackageRegistrar 发布时写入 MeterRegistry."
      }
    }
  ]
}
